title: IRC Archive for channel #xwiki on 11 June 2008 - XWiki
content:
xwikibot - (11/06/2008 09:55): Testpage 1.WebHome was modified by XWiki.mfischer (deleted document) - http://playground.xwiki.org/xwiki/bin/view/Testpage+1/  
marclaporte - (11/06/2008 09:58): vmassol: ping  
vmassol - (11/06/2008 09:58): marclaporte: pong  
marclaporte - (11/06/2008 09:58): ca va?  
vmassol - (11/06/2008 09:59): yep I'm fine thanks  
marclaporte - (11/06/2008 10:00): super! je me demandais si toi ou qqun de xwiki sera à WikiSym?  
vmassol - (11/06/2008 10:10): marclaporte: Stephane Lauriere from XWiki will be at Wkisym. Now I've just remember that today is the last day to submit demos for WikiSym...  
marclaporte - (11/06/2008 10:15): vmassol: thus my presence here :-)  
vmassol - (11/06/2008 10:15): hehe :)  
vmassol - (11/06/2008 10:15): thanks for the reminder then  
vmassol - (11/06/2008 10:16): marclaporte: I think private chat is not working too well on irc.freenode.net, so here is stephane's email: slauriere at xwiki.com  
marclaporte - (11/06/2008 10:21): ok  
marclaporte - (11/06/2008 10:22): you have mail :-)
